    <abstract audience="internal" id="aspace_aa968e3d9efb5b69b5d7c91a603e9272">About 588 travel views from around the world, including North America and Europe, by many well-known early travel photographers such as Francis Frith, James Valentine, George Washington Wilson and Carlo Ponti.</abstract>
